article.description: — Ta'lon Cooper had 11 points and 12 assists to carry Morehead State to a 71-66 win over Presbyterian on Monday night.
article.headline: Cooper lifts Morehead St. over Presbyterian 71-66
article.linkText: Cooper lifts Morehead St. over Presbyterian 71-66
article.story: MOREHEAD, Ky. -- — Ta'lon Cooper had 11 points and 12 assists to carry Morehead State to a 71-66 win over Presbyterian on Monday night. Johni Broome had 17 points and six blocks for the Eagles (6-3), who have won four in a row. Jaylen Sebree added 13 points. Skyelar Potter had six rebounds. Winston Hill had 14 points and seven rebounds for the Blue Hose (6-4). Rayshon Harrison added 13 points and six assists. Trevon Reddish had 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
